	* src/wc_avx2.c (wc_lines_avx2): Change from
	_mm256_sub_epi8() + _mm256_sad_epu8() to
	_mm256_movemask_epi8() + __builtin_popcount().
	This will allow adjusting the I/O size above 16KiB.
